snippet.title: Diana and Roma taste Chocolate Milk Shake
snippet.description:
Diana played toys. The girl wanted sweets. Diana eats a chocolate bar, and brother Roma has the same chocolate milkshake. Diana and Roma taste chocolate milkshakes.
